# aesthetic-core

Shared Python package for CLIP/LAION scoring, aesthetic dissection proxies, and style-alignment metrics.

Used by `AestheticDissectionPanel` and `StyleBallot` in the Deliberative Visual Co-Creation monorepo.

```bash
pip install -e packages/aesthetic_core
```
